{"tid":929982,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【爆相爆片】聖誕男港鐵內情難自禁啜爆「湯洛雯","createTime":"2018-12-06T03:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T02:10:37.000Z","uid":17646,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f75ef65fbfb20639a990ec2f1febab70025432","tid":929982,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T03:26:15.000Z","msg":"「地下鐵碰着她，好比心中女神進入夢&hellip;&hellip;」一個戴住聖誕帽、着橙色格仔恤衫同軍綠色長褲嘅六呎猛男，喺港鐵嘅車廂遇到佢心目中嘅女神，仲情不自禁，走上前輕吻女神嘅前額。畫面就好似童話故事咁浪漫。但如果，佢只係錫女神一張貼喺車廂入面嘅廣告海報，件事係唔係即刻唔同晒？<br />\n<br />\n讀者阿Dan星期一夜晚8點幾，乘搭港鐵港島綫向堅尼地城方向嘅列車期間，聽到有類似跌手機落地嘅聲音，於是向聲音傳嚟嘅方向望過去，畀佢見到一個身高有1.8米嘅男人，眼甘甘望住貼喺車廂入面一張廣告海報，而且仲不斷錫印喺海報上面嘅長髮女代言人。<br />\n<br />\n話說嗰張海報係推銷面膜嘅廣告，搵嚟有「靚湯」之稱、現年31歲嘅無綫小花湯洛雯做代言人影硬照。當時阿Dan同六呎男都有一段距離，睇唔到海報入面令到六呎男如癡如醉嘅女神係邊個，只係覺得佢行為好奇怪，於是離遠攞手機影低佢。從阿Dan拍攝短短18秒嘅短片中，可以見到六呎男都幾癡情，佢拎住個手機，突然間一手撳住海報，跟住咀落海報嘅湯洛雯個前額，錫完一啖，佢情深款款咁望住「靚湯」，然後又繼續連環輕吻「靚湯」三吓，之後繼續定格望住張海報。<br />\n<br />\n阿Dan話六呎男事後仲用手機影低張海報添，而坐喺海報側邊座位嘅女乘客，似乎顧住傾偈，冇為意呢一幕情景。最終阿Dan同六呎男不約而同喺中環站落車，阿Dan見六呎男咁早就戴定聖誕帽，估計佢可能要過一個Lonely Christmas，所以搵廣告海報中嘅女神慰藉一吓喎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181205/large/1544015509_2121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181205%2Flarge%2F1544015509_2121.jpg&h=1c7c8901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181205/58996467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181205%2F58996467&d=35v5%2BV5R0wjNmYl1b1mfCU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=bf5f9add\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181205%2F58996467&h=af9d280e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181205/58996467</a>"},{"pid":"f9e6919b8ebb947158e783feabe5fe11a86af320","tid":929982,"uid":172507,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:31:59.000Z","msg":"發神經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b08e19b5803239ebc4249e3407573ef3beca74c","tid":929982,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810ab1c8d208fc90cab3daf7dc4e081178949030","tid":929982,"uid":146066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"精神病"},{"pid":"c9b789ab002f879ca869e02a0dead481ed6e39f7","tid":929982,"uid":21399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9c313391ef043530b4550b4cb91eec858e344c","tid":929982,"uid":20430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36dyARe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36dyARe.png&h=43e47feb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n活動佈置又咁岩係地鐡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab49ca2304a87386949aa49035e9906b60fef0f","tid":929982,"uid":155137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"22c8fe786b9af9dc914572ee10c7a24656966b44","tid":929982,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:51:03.000Z","msg":"咁湯洛雯真係好正嘛"},{"pid":"a822730735e88a9f9a5fa8768161d9935a9beaa5","tid":929982,"uid":65530,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:53:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59a018b19c4589e8ce69056809a8098cec80ec2d","tid":929982,"uid":2040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:53:49.000Z","msg":"sorry囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb1e8a0e7e59d0a0303afa0eb29e34d56dbeae9","tid":929982,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a822730735e88